OL,3,CAvanti West Coast train managers to
OL,4,Cstrike in dispute over rest day working
OL,6,FTrain managers at Avanti West Coast
OL,7,Fare to strike in a dispute over rest
OL,8,Fday working.
OL,10,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,11,FTransport union will walk out on
OL,12,FDecember 22, 23 and 29.
OL,14,FUnion members voted overwhelmingly
OL,15,Fagainst the company's proposals.
OL,17,FAvanti West Coast has said it is
OL,18,F"disappointed and will continue to
OL,19,Fwork with the union to resolve the
OL,20,Fdispute".
