OL,3,CAvanti West Coast train managers to
OL,4,Cstrike in dispute over rest day working
OL,6,F"It's time for Avanti to put forward
OL,7,Fserious proposals that reflect the
OL,8,Fvital contribution of our train
OL,9,Fmanagers to the railway.
OL,11,F"We remain ready to reach a negotiated
OL,12,Fsettlement and we urge management to
OL,13,Fshow they are serious about resolving
OL,14,Fthis dispute."
OL,16,FAvanti West Coast has issued a
OL,17,Fstatement.
