OL,3,CAvanti West Coast train managers to
OL,4,Cstrike in dispute over rest day working
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "At one of our
OL,7,Fbusiest and most important times of
OL,8,Fthe year when our customers should be
OL,9,Fmaking journeys to visit family or
OL,10,Ffriends during the holiday period,
OL,11,Fthey will now face significant
OL,12,Fdisruption because of these strikes.
